summary: Okay but why did I know that Happy directed Iron Man???
title: Okay but why did I know that Happy directed Iron Man???
body:
We so often credit the MCU to Robert Downey Jr., calling him the Father of the MCU, but I’d argue that Jon Favreau was just as important. Like… HE DIRECTED AND STARRED IN IRON MAN. And his character is pretty fucking important to the MCU. Yeah, he’s more of a background guy, but he’s part of what made Tony… Tony. And he’s still in Marvel movies! He was in Infinity War for crying out loud.

I love RDJ as much as the next person (seriously I love him with all my heart)… but like. We need to give Jon Favreau more credit. 

Just… Jon Favreau guys.
